<text><body>
<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">三　長老之譬喻二</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">第十六　槃多吉瓦迦品</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一六〇　拘物無陀達耶迦（拘物頭布施）</cb:mulu><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.181" type="PTS_hide"></ref><cb:div type="other">
<milestone unit="juan" n="17"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0253a05"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0253a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">第十七　須波離奢利耶</cb:mulu><head>第十七　須波離奢利耶</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0253a07"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0253a08"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0253a09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一六一　須波離奢利耶（善崇敬）</cb:mulu><head>一六一　須波離奢利耶（善崇敬）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0253a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0253a1001">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0253a1001" style="margin-left:3em"><l>稱名鉢頭摩<note n="0253001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">過去二十四佛之第八佛。Buddhavaṁsa 3l; Jātaka I, P, 36。</note>，兩足之尊者，由山傾斜出，說法具眼者。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0253a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0253a1101">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0253a1101" style="margin-left:3em"><l>大仙不遠處，眾多夜叉集，彼等認知佛，己達所當作。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0253a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0253a1201">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0253a1201" style="margin-left:3em"><l>聞不死教法，領會佛所言，心淨吾欣喜，彈指以承侍<note n="0253002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">讀為 upaṭṭhahiṁ（暹羅本）。</note>。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0253a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0253a1301">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0253a1301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>吾承侍尊師，見清淨果報，三萬劫之間，吾不生惡趣。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0253a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0253a1401">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0253a1401" style="margin-left:3em"><l>千九百劫昔，其名喚莊嚴<note n="0253003" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Samalaṅkata（莊嚴）。</note>，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0254a" n="0254a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0254a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0254a0101">六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0254a0101" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0254a02"/><p xml:id="pN29p0254a0201" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者須波離奢利耶長老宣唱此偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0254a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0254a04"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0254a05"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0254a06"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0254a07"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0254a08"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0254a09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一六二　迦那耶羅普毘耶（迦那耶羅花）</cb:mulu><head><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.182"></ref>一六二　迦那耶羅普毘耶（迦那耶羅花）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0254a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0254a1001">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0254a1001" style="margin-left:3em"><l>悉達多世尊，善逝世間解，眾多弟子隨，行步來城中。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0254a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0254a1101">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0254a1101" style="margin-left:3em"><l>吾為王守護，宮中受尊敬<note n="0254001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">在底本已將 āsiṁ-gopako 之連結符——除去。</note>，走近樓閣上，眼見世導師。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0254a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0254a1201">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0254a1201" style="margin-left:3em"><l>迦那耶羅花<note n="0254002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">kanavera（or Kanavīra）屬夾竹桃。</note>，撒向比丘眾，更撒彼佛陀，善撒於其花。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0254a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0254a1301">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0254a1301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>吾供養花朶，九十四劫間，惡趣吾不知，供花此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0254a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0254a1401">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0254a1401" style="margin-left:3em"><l>八十七劫昔，四王大威力，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0255a" n="0255a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0255a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0255a0101">六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0255a0101" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0255a02"/><p xml:id="pN29p0255a0201" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者迦那耶羅普毘耶長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0255a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0255a04"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0255a05"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0255a06"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0255a07"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0255a08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一六三　格奢伽達耶迦（堅果布施）</cb:mulu><head>一六三　格奢伽達耶迦（堅果布施）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0255a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0255a0901">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0255a0901" style="margin-left:3em"><l>向世尊帝沙，吾昔施樹果，那利薊羅施<note n="0255001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">nāḷikera（椰子）。</note>，堅實高貴果。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0255a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0255a1001">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0255a1001" style="margin-left:3em"><l>帝沙佛大仙，吾施彼世尊，如願吾再生，如想得快樂。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0255a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0255a1101">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0255a1101" style="margin-left:3em"><l>彼時布施故，九十二劫間，惡趣吾不知，施果此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0255a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0255a1201">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0255a1201" style="margin-left:3em"><l>十三劫往昔，吾為帝似王<note n="0255002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Indasama（帝似）。</note>，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0255a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0255a1301">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0255a1301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0255a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0255a1401" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者格奢卡伽達耶迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0256a" n="0256a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0256a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0256a02"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0256a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0256a04"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0256a05"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0256a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一六四　提薩普奢伽（處供養）</cb:mulu><head><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.183"></ref>一六四　提薩普奢伽（處供養）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0256a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0256a0701">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0256a0701" style="margin-left:3em"><l>阿塔達西佛，世間居上首，彼佛騰空去，往直風路行。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0256a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0256a0801">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0256a0801" style="margin-left:3em"><l>尊師騰空行，彼大仙足停，彼處吾合掌，清信施供養。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0256a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0256a0901">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0256a0901" style="margin-left:3em"><l>吾見大牟尼，從此千八劫，惡趣吾不知，供養處果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0256a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0256a1001">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0256a1001" style="margin-left:3em"><l>一千百劫昔，名謂牛善生<note n="0256001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Gosujāta（牛善生）。</note>，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0256a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0256a1101">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0256a1101" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0256a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0256a1201" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者提薩普奢伽長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0256a13"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0256a14"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0257a" n="0257a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0257a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0257a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一六五　伽尼伽拉奢達尼耶（伽尼伽拉之繖蓋）</cb:mulu><head>一六五　伽尼伽拉奢達尼耶（伽尼伽拉之繖蓋）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0257a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0257a0301">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0257a0301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>正覺毘舍浮，世間居上首，由白晝居所，移入大森林<note n="0257001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">讀為 ogāhayi（暹羅本）。</note>。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0257a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0257a0401">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0257a0401" style="margin-left:3em"><l>伽尼伽拉花，採摘作繖蓋，並作花鬘覆，以此捧獻佛。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0257a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0257a0501">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0257a0501" style="margin-left:3em"><l>依此獻供花，三十一劫間，惡趣吾不知，供佛此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0257a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0257a0601">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0257a0601" style="margin-left:3em"><l>二十劫往昔，八王黃金光<note n="0257002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Soṇṇābha（黃金光）。</note>，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0257a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0257a0701">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0257a0701" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0257a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0257a0801" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者<note n="0257003" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">此處為 Kaṇikārapupphiya（伽尼伽拉花），但脚註及暹羅本皆與標題同。</note>伽尼伽拉普毘耶長者宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0257a09"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0257a10"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0257a11"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0257a12"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0257a13"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0257a14"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0258a" n="0258a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0258a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0258a02"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0258a03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一六六　薩毘達耶迦（酥布施）</cb:mulu><head><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.184"></ref>一六六　薩毘達耶迦（酥布施）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0258a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0258a0401">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0258a0401" style="margin-left:3em"><l>世尊名普沙<note n="0258001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">讀為 nāmāsi（暹羅本）。</note>，受尊供物人，雄者往行道，清淨眾多人。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0258a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0258a0501">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0258a0501" style="margin-left:3em"><l>世尊次第行，近至吾邊傍，吾受其鉢陀，盛酥油施佛。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0258a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0258a0601">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0258a0601" style="margin-left:3em"><l>爾時施酥故，九十二劫間，惡趣吾不知，施酥油果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0258a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0258a0701">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0258a0701" style="margin-left:3em"><l>五十六劫昔，有名等水王<note n="0258002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Samodaka（等水）。</note>，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0258a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0258a0801">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0258a0801" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0258a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0258a0901" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者薩毘達耶迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0258a10"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0258a11"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0258a12"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0258a13"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0258a14"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0259a" n="0259a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0259a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0259a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一六七　優提迦普毘耶（素馨花）</cb:mulu><head>一六七　優提迦普毘耶（素馨花）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0259a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0259a0301">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0259a0301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>羌達巴伽河，吾沿岸邊行，迎見自存人，如娑羅樹花。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0259a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0259a0401">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0259a0401" style="margin-left:3em"><l>吾持素馨花，拜見大牟尼，清淨心內喜，吾捧花獻佛。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0259a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0259a0501">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0259a0501" style="margin-left:3em"><l>依此花供養，九十四劫間，惡趣吾不知，供佛此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0259a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0259a0601">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0259a0601" style="margin-left:3em"><l>六十七劫昔，一人名濟出<note n="0259001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Samuddhara（濟出）。</note>，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0259a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0259a0701">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0259a0701" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0259a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0259a0801" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者優提迦普毘耶長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0259a09"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0259a10"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0259a11"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0259a12"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0259a13"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一六八　睹薩達耶迦（布布施）</cb:mulu><head><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.185"></ref>一六八　睹薩達耶迦（布布施）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0259a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0259a1401">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0259a1401" style="margin-left:3em"><l>低彌羅市盛，時吾為王子，吾得於供獻，布施靜安人。</l></lg>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0260a" n="0260a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0260a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0260a0101">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0260a0101" style="margin-left:3em"><l>世尊容吾意，以手觸施衣，佛陀納衣後，騰上高空去。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0260a02"/><p xml:id="pN29p0260a0201">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0260a0201" style="margin-left:3em"><l>如是自佛去，施布後追逐，吾心忽清淨，佛為最上人。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0260a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0260a0301">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0260a0301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>爾時施布故，九十四劫間，惡趣吾不知，施布此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0260a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0260a0401">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0260a0401" style="margin-left:3em"><l>六十七劫昔，吾為轉輪王，得名稱清淨<note n="0260001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Parisuddha（清淨）。</note>，力偉大人王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0260a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0260a0501">六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0260a0501" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0260a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0260a0601" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者睹薩達耶迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0260a07"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0260a08"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0260a09"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0260a10"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0260a11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一六九　薩瑪達巴迦（訓示）</cb:mulu><head>一六九　薩瑪達巴迦（訓示）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0260a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0260a1201">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0260a1201" style="margin-left:3em"><l>盤頭摩帝市<note n="0260001-1" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Bandhumatī（親惠城）。</note>，同業大聚會，吾為會頭主，彼等奉事吾。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0260a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0260a1301">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0260a1301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>召集彼大眾，期造增福業：「華鬘施僧團，作無上福田。」</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0260a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0260a1401">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0260a1401" style="margin-left:3em"><l>彼等然允諾，遵從吾意願，眾人備華鬘，布施毘婆尸。</l></lg>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0261a" n="0261a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0261a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0261a0101">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0261a0101" style="margin-left:3em"><l>依此華鬘施，九十一劫間，惡趣吾不知，施華鬘果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0261a02"/><p xml:id="pN29p0261a0201">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0261a0201" style="margin-left:3em"><l>五十九劫昔，出一人中主，大力名花環<note n="0261002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Āveyya 暹羅本為 Āvela（花環），應予採用。</note>，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0261a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0261a0301">六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0261a0301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0261a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0261a0401" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者薩瑪達巴迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0261a05"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0261a06"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0261a07"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0261a08"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0261a09"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0261a10"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一七〇　槃奢古利耶（五指印）</cb:mulu><head><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.186"></ref>一七〇　槃奢古利耶（五指印）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0261a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0261a1101">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0261a1101" style="margin-left:3em"><l>有佛名帝沙<note n="0261001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">讀為 nāmāsi（暹羅本）。</note>，世尊大牟尼，適香殿住居，住此彼牟尼。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0261a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0261a1201">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0261a1201" style="margin-left:3em"><l>吾持香華鬘，往詣尊者前，如不信正覺<note n="0261002-1" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">底本 appasādo va ramuddhe 暹羅本為 appasaddho ca……。</note>，吾施五指印。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0261a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0261a1301">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0261a1301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>彼時捧香故，從此九二劫，吾不知惡趣，施五指印果。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0261a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0261a1401">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0261a1401" style="margin-left:3em"><l>七十二劫昔，有王名自照<note n="0261003" resp="NanChuan" type="orig">[02]</note><note n="0261003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">Sayampabha（自照）。（CBETA 按：漢譯南傳大藏經此頁對應之註標[02]與章節校注內容不符，故今將此處的[02]註標修訂成[03]註標。）</note>，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0262a" n="0262a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0262a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0262a0101">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0262a0101" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0262a02"/><p xml:id="pN29p0262a0201" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者槃古利耶長老宣唱此等偈。</p>
<lb ed="N" n="0262a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0262a04"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0262a05"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0262a06"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0262a07"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0262a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0262a0801" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">攝頌：</p>
<lb ed="N" n="0262a09"/><lg xml:id="lgN29p0262a0901" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:3em">須波離、迦那耶羅、格奢迦、提薩普伽、</l>
<lb ed="N" n="0262a10"/><l style="text-indent:3em">伽尼伽拉、薩毘達、優提迦普、睹薩達、</l>
<lb ed="N" n="0262a11"/><l style="text-indent:3em">瑪拉<note n="0262001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Māla（華鬘）指 Samādapaka 布施之華鬘。</note>、槃奢古利耶、十人共偈五十四偈。</l></lg></cb:div></cb:div>
